{"text_id":122741,"tokens":["In"," this"," work",","," we"," investigate"," the"," kinematic"," decou","pling"," of"," globular"," clusters"," (","GC","s",")"," characterized"," by"," extended"," horizontal","-","branch"," (","E","HB",")"," stars","."," The"," kinematic"," decou","pling"," of"," G","Cs"," has"," been"," a"," problem"," of"," great"," interest"," in"," the"," field"," of"," astro","physics",","," as"," it"," provides"," insights"," into"," the"," formation"," and"," evolution"," of"," these"," stellar"," systems","."," Specifically",","," we"," focus"," on"," the"," relationship"," between"," E","HB"," morphology"," and"," the"," internal"," kinematics"," of"," G","Cs",".","\n\n","The"," motivation"," for"," our"," research"," stems"," from"," the"," increasing"," evidence"," that"," E","HB"," stars"," are"," reliable"," tra","cers"," of"," the"," dynamical"," history"," of"," G","Cs","."," Previous"," studies"," have"," suggested"," that"," E","HB"," stars"," exhibit"," different"," kinematics"," compared"," to"," the"," bulk"," of"," GC"," stars",","," indicating"," a"," possible"," kinematic"," decou","pling","."," However",","," the"," physical"," mechanisms"," responsible"," for"," this"," decou","pling"," remain"," unclear",".","\n\n","Our"," study"," employs"," high","-","precision"," radial"," velocity"," measurements"," of"," E","HB"," stars"," in"," a"," sample"," of"," G","Cs"," with"," varying"," E","HB"," morpho","logies","."," We"," find"," that"," the"," internal"," kinematics"," of"," G","Cs"," with"," E","HB"," stars"," are"," indeed"," decou","pled"," from"," the"," bulk"," of"," the"," cluster","."," Furthermore",","," we"," observe"," a"," significant"," correlation"," between"," the"," E","HB"," morphology"," and"," the"," degree"," of"," kinematic"," decou","pling",","," suggesting"," a"," link"," between"," the"," formation"," of"," E","HB"," stars"," and"," the"," dynamical"," evolution"," of"," G","Cs",".","\n\n","These"," results"," contribute"," to"," our"," understanding"," of"," the"," formation"," and"," evolution"," of"," G","Cs",","," indicating"," a"," complex"," interplay"," between"," stellar"," evolution"," and"," dynamical"," processes"," in"," shaping"," the"," observed"," properties"," of"," these"," ancient"," stellar"," systems","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}